response.original_title: Is the DFB-Pokal the Best Cup Competition in the World?
response.overview: As the 2019/20 DFB-Pokal kicks off, Eli travels to Germany and hits the Autobahn in search of what makes this cup competition so special, taking in three first round matches in three days.
response.title: Is the DFB-Pokal the Best Cup Competition in the World?
